version_description: Includes additional chords, riff and chord legend.
A very simple christmas number one record in the uk,best played on acoustic guitar for a Ciff singalong at christmas.

I use the chords in this version when I'm performing this song live - throw in some Cadd9s for variation on the acoustic guitar and it sounds really nice. I've also written in the timings to the instrumental section which are critical.
In the original key, includes key change for last verse and coda, plus chord legend.
